Thanks for looking into this for me.  Hopefully these answers help.

Is this the index for all products?   Yes,  we would like to have the ability to offer all western Canadian products under this formate.  Under this structure we will be buying/selling natural gas in exchange for "the last scheduled Trading Day of the NYMEX Henry Hub Natural Gas Futures Contract" modified by the price submitted by the counterparty on the website.
Which ones will be the locations you will be using?  We will be putting out AECO, Sumas, Station 2, and Empress products under this format.
Please match a Risk Book assignment to each location	AECO/Empress  - FT-Cand-EGSC and Sumas/Station 2 - FT-Cand-EGSC-BC
Who will be the trader?  Chris Lambie for AECO and Empress; Chris Dorland for Sumas/Station 2
Who will be the risk book administrator?  Chelsea Bardel - (403) 974 6957
What will be the terms trading? We would like to have the ability to set up a bunch of products beyond 1 Month.  To start with: Nov01,Dec01, Nov01-Mar02, Apr02-Oct02, Nov02-Mar03, Apr03-Oct03.

If you need a more through explaination please let me know.

